- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and classification of abusive language on Twitter.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper focuses on detecting abusive language in online social media.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses machine learning algorithms for classification.
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is relevant as the paper deals with social issues related to online abuse and hate speech.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with identifying and classifying specific types of abusive language on Twitter.
